ass="evnt-card-cell members-cell"><p class="members">Members:<span>5157</span></p></div></div></div><div class="evnt-card-body"><div class="evnt-card-table"><div class="evnt-card-cell evnt-info-cell"><div class="evnt-logo-wrapper"><img src="https://d3373sevsv1jc.cloudfront.net/uploads/communities_production/community/logo/33/cf642c76-72fe-49e3-8362-57e86df8b9a3.png" alt="We are Community"></div><div class="evnt-name-wrapper"><h2 data-tooltip-id="community-card-tooltip_33"><span>We are Community</span></h2></div><div class="evnt-description-wrapper"><p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span>Wearecommunity.io is an independent platform for real engineering communities. On Community Platform, we bring together people with common tech-focused interests for any engineer from any domain, country, or company and we believe in a culture of sharing knowledge.</span></p></div><div class="evnt-button-wrapper"><div class="evnt-reg-wrapper"><button type="button" id="02d6010c-7889-405c-8ef8-63991db5ed6a" class="Button-module__button__Oq73a Button-module__small__3KYbo Button-module__grass__LyAs- subscribe reg-button">Join</button></div></div></div></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="evnt-communities-column"><div class="evnt-community-card evnt-banner-card banner-solutions"><a href="https://solutionshub.epam.com/search?mode=solutions&amp;sort=most-popular" target="_blank"><div class="Solutions-module__cardWrapper__xvahO"><div class="Solutions-module__bannerImage__3-RuH Solutions-module__software__2VHrY"></div><div class="Solutions-module__bannerText__7uBka"><h2 class="Solutions-module__title__15b6z">Best EPAM Software and Services</h2><p class="Solutions-module__text__NUMo-">Find the one that meets your needs at EPAM SolutionsHub</p></div><div class="Solutions-module__bannerButton__ME2h9"><button type="button" id="7d860e42-8834-42b3-8e01-26df247ea374" class="Button-module__button__Oq73a Button-module__medium__2vqKz Button-module__white__1XK-v Solutions-module__button__1